@louisryan yep the interval values are valid. 

Due to multiple testing problem, to make a [2.5, 97.5] percentile more statistically valid, you will need a stricter alpha. So the method corrects the interval to become [0.83, 99,16]. Thus the interval values you see is actually "more" valid.

The problem is that it is confusing without explanation. We will think about it and update the method signature.

